Description
-----------

Flags the surface as made of *surfacetype14* to define the type of hit
sound and debris.

Usage
-----

In the global section of your material shader type...

    surfacetype14

Parameters
----------

None.

Notes
-----

The material will play the snd\_surfacetype14 soundshader when shot and
show mtr\_wound\_surfacetype14 as a decal.

